    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal traction. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, maintaining the platform's signature 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. Finished in Carbon Black over a well-preserved interior, this car has been maintained with an emphasis on performance longevity, including recent valve clearances and cooling system overhaul. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car ready for the canyons.",
