    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained Lexus RX 350 strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest signs of a vehicle that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the parchment leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of premium tires installed last season. It drives straight and smooth, offering the quiet, composed ride these models are famous for. This is a dependable, attractive vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
